*Story**

Once upon a time in a forest,there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon tree, which was on a banks of river. 
In the same forest there lived a Crocodile and his wife.One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under
the tree.The kind hearted monkey affered him some fruits.The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them.
As days passed by the crocodile and monkey became good friends....

One day the monkey sent some fruits for the crocodile's wife. She ate the fruits and loved them but was jealous as she did not 
like her husband spending time with a monkey. She told her husband that if the fruits are so juicy, I wonder how sweet the would 
the monkey's heart will be. She wanted to get her the heart of the monkey .The crocodile was not willing to kill his friend but 
he has no choice.
